Body: Description: receiving a 503 error when trying to get to the access tab in the reporting website page

+++++

2024_1212:

+++++

+++++

Reference install doc for AIC 11.5

+++++

STEPS PERFORMED

+++++

1) Uninstalled AIC 11.5 through Control Panel (or appwiz.cpl)

2) Installed AIC on the D: drive into "wwwrootinetpub" directory

3) AIC was installed on the following ports:

http:81

https:8082 - SUCCESS - BOA was able to access the Access tab (Reports tab on LEFT, Access TAB on the RIGHT).

+++++
